relatedBlades.subtitle: Cloudflare users like you share their story

features.title: Bannerflow
features.description: Kasper Purunen, Engineering Manager at Bannerflow, shares how the Swedish SaaS platform benefits from Cloudflare's ease of use and fast delivery speeds

features.title: Campaign Genius
features.description: Matthew Dunn, founder and CTO of Campaign Genius speaks to the speed, agility, and cost-effectiveness from shifting web apps to the edge with Cloudflare

features.title: Chainshot Filmproduktion
features.description: Florian Klaes, film producer at Chainshot Filmproduktion in Germany, shares his experience using Cloudflare Stream to accelerate the performance of his website and deliver a pleasant experience for prospects viewing video content

features.title: Doll Divine
features.description: Founder of DollDivine.com, Ola Rogula, shares how using Cloudflare is like having a whole web team without actually having one

features.title: Giobi Fasoli
features.description: Hear from Giobi Fasoli from giobi.com, a freelance web developer in Italy on how easy it is to quickly configure domains with Cloudflare

features.title: Halborn
features.description: David Schwed, COO of Halborn, shares how they use Cloudflare to increase the performance of their site and defend against bad actors

features.title: Happy Cog
features.description: Matt Weinberg, President of Technology at Happy Cog, shares how Cloudflare helps them support major clients like ProPublica

features.title: Jeff Powell
features.description: Jeff Powell runs his personal website with Cloudflare and enjoys the high availability, performance and savings on egress costs

features.title: mogenius
features.description: Hear from Gerrit Schumann, CEO of mogenius on how the company has integrated Cloudflare in their cloud infrastructure for optimal security and performance

features.title: Moneybox
features.description: Jonathan Leigh at Moneybox, an award-winning digital wealth manager, shares his experience with Cloudflare Zero Trust

features.title: MonsieurChalets
features.description: Raphaël Tremblay-Bouchard, Product Owner at MonsieurChalets shares how Cloudflare helped him to increase site speed and bookings

features.title: New York Road Runners
features.description: Diego Marin from New York Road Runners, the organization behind the New York City Marathon, shares his experience with Cloudflare Zero Trust

features.title: Nodecraft
features.description: James Ross, CTO of Nodecraft, shares how his team uses Cloudflare Workers to rapidly develop and deploy applications faster than ever before

features.title: Padlet
features.description: Nitesh Goel, CEO of Padlet, shares how they simplify video delivery with Cloudflare Stream

features.title: StudyHall
features.description: Hear from Michael Young, Founder of StudyHall, on how he uses Cloudflare to accelerate the web production process and secure StudyHall from attacks

features.title: Supabase
features.description: Supabase engineer, Inian Parameshwaran, shares their journey as they grew from solely being a Cloudflare DNS user to now using Workers, app security, and more

features.title: Taurus
features.description: Sébastien Pasche, VP of Engineering at Taurus, shares how the company protects its SaaS and managed services operations with Cloudflare Argo Smart Routing

features.title: Tropee
features.description: Moein Akbarof, Application architect at Tropee, uses Cloudflare to deliver faster site performance and protection against malicious bots

features.title: Uniswap Labs
features.description: Connor McEwen from Uniswap Labs discusses his excitment about having IPFS Gateway to support running Ethereum nodes

features.title: WP Engine
features.description: Ellie Cooper from WP Engine shares how partnering with Cloudflare enables the organization to optimize its WordPress hosting services
